	For other Sina coverage, see Sina.xml.



	CDN buckets:

		- js.app.ccgslb.com.cn

			- img.app.wcdn.cn
			- img1.app.wcdn.cn

		- u1.sinaimg.cn.cdngc.net


	Nonfunctional domains:

		- u1.sinaimg.cn		(403; mismatched, CN: *.pantherssl.com)
		- img.app.wcdn.cn	(403; mismatched, CN: support4.cdnetworks.net)
		- img[12].app.wcdn.cn	(403; mismatched, CN: *.pantherssl.com)
		- e.weibo.com
		- game.weibo.com
		- open.weibo.com


	Problematic subdomains:

		- hr			(mismatched, CN: *.sinaapp.com)
